      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p>We are pleased to announce that Liferay DXP Quarterly Release 2025.Q4 is now available for download.<br>\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>The key highlights for this Quarterly Release are:</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>New Liferay Headless CMS - <span class=\"ml-rte-link-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/e/release-notes/release-highlights/20004/27025760?r=27025760#:~:text=Management%20System%20(CMS)-,New%20Liferay%20Headless%20CMS,-With%20Liferay%27s%20New\">Learn More</a></span></li>\n\t<li>Composable Account Selector - <span class=\"ml-rte-link-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/e/release-notes/release-highlights/20004/27025760?r=27025760#Composable%20Account%20Selector:~:text=Commerce-,Composable%20Account%20Selector,-A%20new%20set\">Learn More</a></span></li>\n\t<li>Upgrade Process Automated Database Repair - <span class=\"ml-rte-link-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/e/release-notes/release-highlights/20004/27025760?r=27025760#Upgrade%20Process%20Automated%20Database%20Repair:~:text=Platform-,Upgrade%20Process%20Automated%20Database%20Repair,-The%20Liferay%20database\">Learn More</a></span></li>\n\t<li>Liferay DXP MCP Server - <span class=\"ml-rte-link-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/e/release-notes/release-highlights/20004/27025760?r=27025760#:~:text=Integration-,Liferay%20DXP%20MCP%20Server,-An%20MCP%20Server\">Learn More</a></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>To learn more about all the new features available in 2025.Q4 Quarterly Release, please review the <a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/e/release-notes/release-highlights/20004/27025760?r=27025760\">Release Notes</a>.</p>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://customer.liferay.com/downloads/-/download/dxp-2025-q4-0-quarterly-release\">View Available Downloads</a></h3>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/anatomy-of-a-quarterly-release\"><strong><u>Anatomy of a Quarterly Release</u></strong></a><br>\nLearn more about the file and folder structures for Quarterly Releases.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/liferay-dxp-quarterly-release-process\"><strong><u>Frequently Asked Questions</u></strong></a><br>\nSee more important information about our DXP Platform versioning and release cadence.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/liferay-dxp-2025.q4-compatibility-matrix\"><strong><u>DXP 2025.Q4 Compatibility Matrix</u></strong></a><br>\nCheck compatibility here to ensure a smooth and&nbsp;supported upgrade</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/w/dxp/self-hosted-installation-and-upgrades\"><strong><u>Installation Instructions</u></strong></a><br>\nLearn how to install DXP Quarterly Releases.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"
      },
